{"title":"天安门广场","authors":["刘立中"],"dates":[{"year":1997,"month":7,"day":5}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"天安门广场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘立中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那遥远的他乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又来到天安门前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手表，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准北京时间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仰望城楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中升起一种庄严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种责任，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一种回归家园的自豪感。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有阵阵强劲的风吹来："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟着热情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挟着坦诚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定的信仰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"构筑成整个广场；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光弥漫在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国的大陆和天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场上的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都能感受到彼此在沟通……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场广阔无边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿行在人海中间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拍照、留连，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论前辈后辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不分百姓官员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我喜欢这普通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我喜欢这平凡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不再是站在大洋对岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咀嚼着思念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚踏热土，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是中华民族的一员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心像太阳一样灿烂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广场上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬着我们的红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗底下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们在塑造着自己。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南来的风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北来的气息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"振奋着每一颗心："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到神奇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充满自信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像种子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"播撒在春天里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：四川江油市长钢集团公司）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":7,"page_end":7}